{
  "chapter": 16,
  "chapter_summary": "第十六回\"错综复杂\"：胡铁花被平姑娘带入地下石室，与苏蓉蓉、李红袖、宋甜儿、黑珍珠重逢。众女向胡铁花讲述被李玉函、柳无眉夫妻用迷药囚禁的经过。李红袖等人对楚留香安危极为关切，苏蓉蓉识破胡铁花欲隐瞒凶讯的心思。此时李玉函与柳无眉突然出现，柳无眉竟持匕首要自尽，李玉函拼死阻止，二人表现出深挚情感，令众人困惑。关键时刻楚留香现身，揭示李观鱼因练功走火全身僵木，被儿子李玉函假传圣旨利用。楚留香逐步推理，揭露柳无眉实为石观音门下弟子——她既能轻车熟路出入石观音秘谷，又能解石观音独门毒酒，证明她与石观音关系匪浅。柳无眉的身世之谜由此揭开。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "不错，我正是胡铁花，想不到你居然还认得我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "我也知道你是苏蓉蓉，你是李红袖，你是宋甜儿，我以前看到你们时，你们还是小孩子，想不到现在已长得这么大了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "每个人都会长大的，是么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "我早就想看看你们了，只可惜现在这时候真不好，这地方更坏。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ping_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "平姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们老朋友见面，多聊聊吧!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你怎会也到这里来了呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "我也正想问你们是怎么会到这里来的?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我睇去佐沙漠，睇见各匹马翻黎，以为祷……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我说话你恐怕也不懂，还是让她们说吧!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "长话短说，总之我们到沙漠去玩了一趟，就回来找楚留香，却在半路上遇见李玉函、柳无眉夫妻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你们可认得这夫妻两人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "谁认得他们呀!只不过那天我们到快意楼去找小孟尝打听消息的时候，他们恰巧也在那里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们只怕并不是恰巧在那里，而是故意在那里等着你们的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我们本来就觉得这夫妻两人看来人蛮不错的样子，又听说他们是很有名的世家子弟，自然就不会对他们有提防之心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你若是不知道他们的为人，你会对他们有提防之心么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "我也不会，只因为我们都没有楚留香聪明，也没有他那么仔细。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "就因为这缘故，所以他要我们一路同行，我们就答应了，谁知他们竟在我们茶壶里偷偷放了迷药，等我们醒来时，已被送到这里，我实在想不到像他们这样的世家子弟，也会耍如此卑鄙无耻的手段。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "若换了我，我也想不到的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "最奇怪的是，我们到现在为止，还不知道他们究竟存的是什么心，只因我们被关在这里之后，竟一直都没有见到他们。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这小鬼虽然天天骂，天天吵，但无论她怎么骂，李家的人竟好像全都死光了，连一个都不肯露面，我们气极了，就在墙上画了三个大乌龟，谁知他们竟像是真的变成了缩头乌龟，躲着不敢见人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你想，他们这究竟是在打什么主意呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你是不是已见过楚留香了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "我已见过了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他现在究竟在什么地方?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "我……我也不太清楚。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你一定知道的，我希望你莫要瞒着我们，无论他发生了什么事，都希望你告诉我们，因为我们有权知道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他究竟出了什么事?你不说我就先杀了你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "text": "放开他，放开他……他绝没有恶意。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "但他为什么不肯说?他究竟想隐瞒什么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道他不肯说，只不过是怕我们伤心而已。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你这恶贼，你居然还敢来见我们?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你把我们的楚留香怎么样了?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhen_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑珍珠",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你最好快快杀了我，否则我迟早总有一天要杀了你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "恶贼，你敢和我一决生死么?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "都是我害了你，都是我害了你。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你怎么能这样做?快住手。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "我已拖累你这么久，求求你，让我死吧，我死了之后，别人就会原谅你的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你死了之后，我还能活下去么?",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我又怎么舍得离开你?只不过，我觉得你已为我牺牲得太多了，我怎忍再让你陪着我受苦?",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "自从你来了之后，我每一天、每一个时辰都是快乐的，怎么能说是受苦?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "那么，我们不如走吧!去找个地方，安安静静的住下来，不论什么人都不见。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "我也许还能活几个月，等这几个月……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我无论如何也不能让你死，我要你永远活下去。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "可是现在……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "现在我们并没有绝望，我们至少还有这五个人在手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "站住，你若敢再往前走，我就要他们的命。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "到了现在你还不肯放手么?你这是何苦?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香是你么?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老臭虫，你果然没有死，我就知道你死不了的，天下有谁能要你的命?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "但这次若非有人救我，我的命就已经被人要去了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "真有人来救了你?是谁?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你猜不出。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我实在猜不出。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你自然猜不出，只因我自己也想不到，救我的人竟然会是李观鱼李老前辈。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "儿子想要你的命，老子怎会去救你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他根本不知道这件事，更没有要我命的意思，所有的事，全都是这位李公子贤伉俪两人安排出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是，帅一帆那些人，岂非全是受了李观鱼所托而来的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这只不过是李公子在假传圣旨而已，儿子替老子说话，别人自然是不会怀疑的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么李观鱼为何不否认?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "只因李老前辈七年前练功岔了气，全身都已僵木，连话都说不出了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他既已全身僵木，又怎能出手救你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "李老前辈一生正直，最重江湖道义，他眼看着不平的事在他跟前发生，而且还假借他的名字，心里的难受和气愤，你我只怕是想像不到的，但他却又偏偏只能眼睁睁地望着，连动都不能动。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "莫非是他气极之下，那一股久已被憋死的真气，竟又被怒火所激动了么?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "后面的事，你不说我也知道了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "柳无眉正要杀你时，瞧见李老前辈忽然又能走动说话了，自然要大吃一惊，一个人眼见自己的阴谋就要被揭穿，谁都会害怕的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "等她再想杀你时，那五个老头子自然就不会再让她下手，那时李玉函只怕史吓得连魂郡没有了，所以立刻就追到这里来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "十成中你居然猜中了九成，这倒真难得的很。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你既然能找到这里，为什么不将那几个上了当的老头子也带来呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我自己的事，自然还是应该由我自己来解决。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你能解决得了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我也不知道世上是否真的有解决不了的事，至少我到目前还未遇见过。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你们说完了么?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你难道也想说话?好，那么我先问你，楚留香究竟和你有什么仇恨?你为什么要如此害他?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他和我往日无冤，近日无仇，我要杀他，实在情不得已。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你这是在说话，还是在放屁?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "有许多事，我也知道你绝不会懂的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "有许多事我本来的确百思不得其解，可是现在却渐渐想通了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "最令我想不通的就是，你们既然救过我，为什么又要杀我呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "后来我才想通这道理，因为我已发现你们根本没有救过我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你难道忘了那天在石观音的秘谷中……",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "不错，那天你的确杀了不少人，但却并不是为了救我，只因那时我已经逃出来了，你不杀那些人我也可以逃得出去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你既不肯承我的情，我也没法子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你虽未救过我，我还是很感激你，只因若非你出手相救，龟兹王父女和胡铁花他们只怕已死于石观音的毒酒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你居然还未忘记这件事，倒也难得的很。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我自然不会忘记，因为我一直在奇怪，你们是见到苏蓉蓉她们之后到沙漠去的，怎会一到沙漠，就能找得到石观音那秘谷里?那秘谷不但地势偏僻，人迹罕至，而且谷中道路错综复杂，但你们却像是轻车熟路，来去自如，这岂非是件怪事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，听你这么一说，我也觉得奇怪了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "还有，石观音用毒的功夫极精，她配制出来的毒酒，别人自然无法化解，所以她瞧见胡铁花他们喝了她的毒酒后，就立刻走了，因为她认为世上绝没有人能解得了他们的毒，所以才会那么放心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "但你却轻描淡写的就将他们中的毒解了，这岂非又是件怪事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，她若不知道石观音那种酒的毒性，怎么能为我们解毒呢?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这两年事你难道……难道已经想通了么?",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "这两件事虽然很难解释，但却也是你们留下来的惟一漏洞，若非这两件事，我只怕永远也猜不出你的真实身份。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你现在难道已猜出了我真实的身份?",
      "tone": "颤抖",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我先问你，一个人若是根本就没有去过石观音那秘谷，他能在谷中来去自如么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "一个人若不知道石观音那杯毒酒的成分，能解得了那杯酒的毒么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "若非是石观音很亲近的人，既无法知道那秘谷的出入道路，也不会知道那毒酒的成分，是么?",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她……她究竟是什么人呢?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你难道还想不到她也是石观音的门下弟子?",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她若也是石观音门下子弟，那天为何要将她的同门全都杀死?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "石观音既然已经想到龟兹国去称王称霸了，带着这么多徒弟，岂非反成了累赘?",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你……你认为那是石观音要她将那些人杀死的么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 16,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    }
  ],
